\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5dCmh2k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5dCmh2k.jpg&h=274a80cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81b862719d8ed40f5f4d8d64521bf32d12a1b4f2","tid":1509924,"uid":134840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:42:49.000Z","msg":"澄清左啦傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請使用不推文回覆功能"},{"pid":"21afee3dedf9f8183e537275d136fe354a3603bf","tid":1509924,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"387c1b279a1f5b7e8f7db5590ae5e18877114350","tid":1509924,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"8920dc761c4ed6a78605af0caf75eb4e6851efb6","tid":1509924,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/27/qy1R6Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F27%2Fqy1R6Z.jpg&h=5ef8383a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母民主黨賣香港<br />\n<br />\n次次都關鍵時刻出賣香港人<br />\n<br />\n死仆街根本係共產黨卧底！！！！<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚嬲呀屌！！！</span></span>"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:15:17.000Z","msg":"楊衛隆：<br />\n建制販民六傻去到美國與新中共美國國會議員見面。六傻知道要阻止香港人權及民主法通過，一定要跟茶黨談。可是，見茶黨老大要有茶友帶路，中共港共無法接觸茶黨老大。單純接觸幾位親港共眾議員沒用。<br />\n六傻去美國不是阻止美國眾議院通過香港人權及民主法而是將立法程序拖到十一月才正式表決。六傻掛著香港立法會兩大黨派議員招牌在美國招搖撞騙，大話連篇。真的有機會令到眾議院內部爭議不絕，拖慢立法程序。要拖，很容易，拿一大疊文件出來說三道四就可以一日拖一日。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建制販民的盤算是拖到十一月，開開心心過了十一國慶，然後利用大規模搜捕示威者拖垮反送中運動，連讓步都免談。抓一千人不能平息示威，抓一萬人總可以吧。抓一萬人不行，抓十萬。</span></span><br />\n建制販民去到美國，將大疊文件交給美國眾議員，以香港議員身份反對成立香港人權及民主法，要求召開聽證會表達香港民意。單是這些文件和聽證會可以搞一兩個月。到了十一月，反送中示威搞散了，成立香港人權及民主法的必要性也沒有了。搞散香港示威之後再搞散英美共管香港。建制販民真係好陰毒。最毒係兩黨派一齊去美國扮成代表全香港民意。今次大鑊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/189060481135806/posts/3047505011957991?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F189060481135806%2Fposts%2F3047505011957991%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrs3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=283e3a51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/189060481135806/posts/3047505011957991?sfns=mo</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:42:54.000Z","msg":"好地地要同葉劉去見美國官員<br />\n都知呢排撚屌唔方好人"},{"pid":"5890b01ac200e17282e717967835f0f936b6491f","tid":1509924,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8920dc761c4ed6a78605af0caf75eb4e6851efb6","tid":1509924,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/27/qy1R6Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F27%2Fqy1R6Z.jpg&h=5ef8383a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母民主黨賣香港<br />\n<br />\n次次都關鍵時刻出賣香港人<br />\n<br />\n死仆街根本係共產黨卧底！！！！<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚嬲呀屌！！！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:44:29.000Z","msg":"十幾個post講緊仲澄清埋喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2efab57e77216efe36fc438d1dc3291976d547","tid":1509924,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"387c1b279a1f5b7e8f7db5590ae5e18877114350","tid":1509924,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"8920dc761c4ed6a78605af0caf75eb4e6851efb6","tid":1509924,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/27/qy1R6Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F27%2Fqy1R6Z.jpg&h=5ef8383a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母民主黨賣香港<br />\n<br />\n次次都關鍵時刻出賣香港人<br />\n<br />\n死仆街根本係共產黨卧底！！！！<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚嬲呀屌！！！</span></span>"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:15:17.000Z","msg":"楊衛隆：<br />\n建制販民六傻去到美國與新中共美國